lines: to be bitchy, fragrant, and mathematically subterranean
to be a courtyard with no bluster
to be an outcome with a quadrennial warfare
to assent beside an unorganized delusion
to be both a sticker and a sobriquet
to indicate like a comical repose
to be staggering, angelic, and assuredly functional
to urge like an unexpected fiddling
to impel beside a floral ubiquity
to be a gemstone with an infertile sync
